    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund free public transport free for 18 and under",
        "additional_details": "I want this to be changed because I have a personal experience of the expenses of public transport in the UK. I live in Newcastle and the charges are ridiculous, over \u00a35 for a 16 year old to travel round Newcastle on a metro to get to college. How are the people who don\u2019t have the greatest amount of money supposed to get around?",
        "background": "I want the government to fund free public transport for everyone aged 18 and under, to make it easier for youths to get around where they need to go.",
